{"tid":365182,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Minecraft] 有鳩唔fing, 你做女人呀?","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T06:22:05.000Z","uid":66938,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbd73fe1d124d15e7fcfab61fedc02b9c0f3fc1","tid":365182,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"日日打LOL都打到悶?<br />\nPS4/switch d game又唔岩玩?<br />\n想休閒鳩fing下?<br />\n我地lihk9fingfing 絕對係你首選<br />\n我地係一個輕鬆hea鳩鳩既休閒生存ser<br />\n歡迎各路巴打一齊入黎鳩fing fing <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nversion 是 <span style=\"color: orange;\">1.12</span><br />\n有白名單,請留下你的名字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後一般既essential plugins 都有<br />\n之後有<span style=\"color: orange;\">資源世界,</span>希望大家盡量去番資源世界挖野<br />\n一開波生存起家挖少少無咩所謂<br />\n盡量唔好挖太爛就ok, OP有d強逼症<br />\n各種farm亦都齊哂,大家唔洗再愁無材料<br />\n<br />\n設定<br />\n1. 防火防爆防跌裝, creeper 同TNT會爆炸,會有傷害,但唔會爆到block<br />\n<br />\n2. 一般既大路指令都有,<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">/spawn /sethome /home /tpa /bal </span>等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每人可以set 5 個home, set唔同世界都得</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 有<span style=\"color: teal;\"> /co i </span>可以check 箱有無俾人偷野<br />\n亦有lockette 可以鎖箱share箱俾特定人士<br />\n<br />\n4. SPAWN 有 傳送門 區域<br />\n送你直達不同世界既角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 有經濟系統,可以用<span style=\"color: teal;\">/bal</span> 睇<br />\n新人入ser都會拎到 <span style=\"color: gold;\">$5000</span><br />\n賺錢除左同玩家交易之外,亦可以賣野俾ser<br />\nser 係無限收你d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n努力挖垃圾賣 富可敵國不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 有<span style=\"color: pink;\">Lift plugin </span>, 只要兩個木牌,兩粒制,一個鐵磚,一塊玻璃 就可以<br />\n高度限制都係3格先起到部Lift<br />\n<br />\n7. 有<span style=\"color: red;\">紅石連閃限制</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時未有創造世界,但往後日子可能會整一個<br />\n睇下大家既反應再算<br />\n<br />\n紅石方面,由於server仲係細ser<br />\nRAM數有限,請大家自律建設<br />\n盡量唔好有大型紅石/連閃<br />\n亦唔好騷擾到其他玩家<br />\n多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsub domain : <a href=\"http://lihk.mcph.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flihk.mcph.co&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqEU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=43fd5c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihk.mcph.co</a><br />\n<br />\n而家有discord group<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/sXKC37E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FsXKC37E&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqEU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8202b5da\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/sXKC37E</a><br />\n有大量資訊係入面<br />\n唔用mic 都可以睇到<br />\n齊來吹水吧"},{"pid":"a8c3b8a4e384491185bc3b5773ce830966defe9b","tid":365182,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"Spawn : 天空之城<br />\n入面有官方商店, 亦開放左位置俾玩家進駐<br />\n有哂傳送門送大家到各mob farm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152416_0a15afc49252258b6e7c0821c3499d3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152416_0a15afc49252258b6e7c0821c3499d3d.png&h=c43b869b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152432_36bbb1d437f452add62d3bf604c43334.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152432_36bbb1d437f452add62d3bf604c43334.png&h=c76afc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152447_a0fc2c4834bcc34a00d09ff3ea9b335f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152447_a0fc2c4834bcc34a00d09ff3ea9b335f.png&h=82edc059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152454_adda57714903bd673a766219c55e39a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152454_adda57714903bd673a766219c55e39a8.png&h=63423813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想挑戰自己?<br />\n有競技場,挑戰擊退10/ 速度+10% 等等既怪物<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152513_bc75b377bdb8c161751b39ee0052ef05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152513_bc75b377bdb8c161751b39ee0052ef05.png&h=a36284af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152530_920ced90463a8584bb299f9df3396916.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152530_920ced90463a8584bb299f9df3396916.png&h=03b8d719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152551_b1b3139def10080e83d59d0ce949b114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152551_b1b3139def10080e83d59d0ce949b114.png&h=8f8a3201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152608_debe8c8a1ea252ccb1e16b175c09327a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152608_debe8c8a1ea252ccb1e16b175c09327a.png&h=fae54546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152625_9400c1a5aaed68ebf740f7bb8b834ef5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152625_9400c1a5aaed68ebf740f7bb8b834ef5.png&h=3f373ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想要骨粉,要免費弓,免費箭?<br />\n有 白骨洞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152633_e2931d2036ba9ccac4ca6dce11c860d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152633_e2931d2036ba9ccac4ca6dce11c860d9.png&h=70b669e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資源世界 - 沙漠之都, 沙城<br />\n資源世界座落係數種不同生態既區既交界<br />\n有沙漠/平原/高山 等等, 想挖咩都係哂左近<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152652_eecb5a1f2fc0f2f87bd9d6538c404ecd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152652_eecb5a1f2fc0f2f87bd9d6538c404ecd.png&h=11181b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主世界(生存世界) - 火炎山<br />\n紅砂岩區, 唔鐘意紅砂岩都無問題<br />\n行前少少就有Savanna 大草原俾你玩<br />\n紅砂岩隔離亦有雪原你玩<br />\n冰火七重天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  任你自己揀 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/152641_2f874a81d3b770ac0ccb995d867a5f42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F152641_2f874a81d3b770ac0ccb995d867a5f42.png&h=9017bf27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a161bb86938c5c1481eaf7c924f3d93029b4d4bd","tid":365182,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67a110d194c98b9a0d754e24dba792d75b38f1a","tid":365182,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8962c518cac0edf459761e8889c61246472ab773","tid":365182,"uid":66938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=